sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Claude
    participant Hook as UserPromptSubmit Hook
    participant FS as File System
    participant Command as ArcKit Command

    User->>Claude: /arckit:traceability
    Claude->>Hook: Fire hook (sync)
    Hook->>Hook: Parse arguments from prompt
    Hook->>FS: Scan projects/ for REQ files
    Hook->>FS: Extract requirement IDs (regex)
    Hook->>FS: Scan ADRs/vendors for references
    Hook->>Hook: Compute coverage metrics
    Hook->>Claude: Inject additionalContext with tables
    Claude->>Command: Execute with pre-extracted data
    Command->>Command: Build matrix using hook tables
    Command->>Command: Skip Read operations (data already present)
    Command->>User: Write TRAC file, show summary
